items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 105 distinct venues!

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 25 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 6!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 225 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 46!
Load up those hops, watch the IBU grow and drink it down! Now you’re all hopped up. The more bitter, the better. That's 65 different beers with an IBU of 65 or higher. Try 5 more for Level 14!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 145 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 30!
